doc.previous: Each borough is governed by a Borough Council German Bezirksversammlung and administered by a Municipal Administrator German Bezirksamtsleiter The boroughs are not independent municipalities their power is limited and subordinate to the Senate of Hamburg The borough administrator is elected by the Borough Council and thereafter requires confirmation and appointment by Hamburg s Senate 38 The quarters have no governing bodies of their own
doc.after: In 2008 the boroughs were Altona Bergedorf Eimsb ttel Hamburg Mitte Hamburg Nord Harburg and Wandsbek 41
